telepon dari nomor tak dikenal.

00:10:25.600 --> 00:10:26.760
Mungkin ini darurat.

00:10:26.920 --> 00:10:29.120
Teman-teman, aku akan segera kembali.
- Oke.

00:10:34.040 --> 00:10:36.120
Halo?  - Aniruddha.. Hai.

00:10:37.400 --> 00:10:38.960
