Jhanak!  Selamat ulang tahun!

00:16:14.520 --> 00:16:15.520
Rahul..

00:16:18.840 --> 00:16:19.760
Ani!

00:16:20.320 --> 00:16:21.920
Tinggal satu menit lagi.
Silakan kembali sekarang.

